name: Baby Narwhal (Dream)
description: I encountered a baby narwhal in my dream last night. Incredibly cute, playful plump little thing. Magical. It engaged with me. I tried to take a pic on my phone (I was also talking on the phone describing the creature but called it a “baby beluga”) but it shied away right then, imprinting on a passing orca, following it out of sight. I fell in the water, waist deep, wet pants, climbed out. 4-9-21, @void_denizen
